Analytics
This site uses Plausible Analytics, a privacy-friendly, cookieless web-analytics service self-hosted at analytics.hellebo.de. Plausible:

does not use cookies and does not persist any identifier in the browser;
does not collect personal data, cross-site profiles, or device fingerprints;
aggregates page views, referrers, and outbound-link clicks at the request level only.

The processed data are anonymised aggregates used to understand which pages are useful. Disable JavaScript or use a content blocker to opt out.
